Description: Applies 'AAGI' external brand guidelines to graphics. 'AAGI'
    colours and font guidelines are applied as useful and reasonable to
    both base graphics as well as 'ggplot2' figures.  Support for creating
    MS Word and PowerPoint files using Quarto and RMarkdown templates is
    also provided.
